EN: On New Year's Eve, people light fireworks to celebrate.

ZH: 焰火在黑夜中绽放出美丽的光芒。
EN: The fireworks burst into beautiful lights in the dark night.

ZH: 孩子们都聚集在一起观看焰火。
EN: Children gather together to watch the fireworks.

